## Derived Event Types

### Window Events — `ApplicationEvent.h`

#### `WindowResizeEvent`
```cpp
class PIGEON_API WindowResizeEvent
    : public EventClassCategory<EventCategoryApplication>
    , public EventClassType<EventType::WindowResize>
{
public:
    WindowResizeEvent(unsigned int width, unsigned int height);
    unsigned int GetWidth()  const;
    unsigned int GetHeight() const;
    std::string  ToString()  const override; // "WindowResizeEvent: W, H"
};
```

#### `WindowCloseEvent`
```cpp
class PIGEON_API WindowCloseEvent
    : public EventClassType<EventType::WindowClose>
    , public EventClassCategory<EventCategoryApplication>
{
public:
    WindowCloseEvent();
};
```
No payload — the fact of closure is the entire message.

